<tbody>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
[a]:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Strana kolesa 4. rýchlostného stupňa
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
[c]:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Vyčnievajúci koniec
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
[b]:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Strana krátkej príruby
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0">
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Pomocou špeciálneho nástroja a hydraulického lisu namontujte pravé ložisko (1) na vstupný hriadeľ (2).
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5B022">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09913-80113">
09913–80113
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I3RH0A520019.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "50.069mm" ver = "01" gw = "76" gh = "125"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Namontujte ihličkové ložisko kolesa 3. rýchlostného stupňa (4), namažte ho olejom, potom namontujte koleso 3. rýchlostného stupňa (1) a synchronizačný krúžok (2).
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Pomocou špeciálnych nástrojov a hydraulického lisu nasuňte zostavu objímky a náboja synchronizácie vysokých prevodových stupňov (3).
</ptxt>
<attention3>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Uistite sa, že drážky pre západky krúžku synchronizácie (2) sú zarovnané s perami (5) na zostave objímky a náboja.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Po zalisovaní telesa objímky a náboja skontrolujte, či sa koleso 3. rýchlostného stupňa voľne otáča.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention3>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5B023">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09913-84510">
09913–84510
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A520027.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "99.258mm" ver = "01" gw = "192" gh = "265"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
