[a]:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Strana kolesa 3. rýchlostného stupňa
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
[c]:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Dlhá príruba
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
[b]:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Dráha západky
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Poriadne namontujte poistný krúžok (1) do drážky.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1 page = "2">
<ptxt>
Nainštalujte ihlové ložisko (2) namazané olejom, a potom nainštalujte krúžok synchronizácie (3) a koleso 4. prevodového stupňa.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH01520052.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "45.751mm" ver = "01" gw = "170" gh = "113"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "1.094in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
5.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Vstupný hriadeľ
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Pomocou špeciálneho nástroja a hydraulického lisu zalisujte ľavé ložisko (2).
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5B024">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09913-80113">
09913–80113
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Pomocou toho istého špeciálneho nástroja ako v kroku 10) namontujte rozperu kolesa 5. prevodového stupňa (1).
</ptxt>
<attention2>
<ptxt>
Rozperu kolesa 5. prevodového stupňa (1) nezalisujte spoločne s ľavým ložiskom (2) naraz, aby sa nadmernou kompresiou nezdeformovala.
</ptxt>
</attention2>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I3RH0A520020.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "59.848mm" ver = "01" gw = "182" gh = "153"/>
</figure>
</s1>
